short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: File filter for GitHub code reviews as a Chrome extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Octofilter is an extension that allows you to hide or collapse changes for certain file extensions when doing code reviews on GitHub.

Octofilter is not affiliated with GitHub.
